The following percentages of quantities covered by import licence applications submitted in respect of the period 1 April to 30 June 2002 under the quotas referred to in Regulation (EC) No 1279/98 may be allowed:
(a) 100 % of quantities covered by applications in respect of products falling within CN codes 0201 and 0202 originating in Hungary, the Czech Republic and Slovakia;
(b) 100 % of quantities covered by applications in respect of products falling within CN codes 0201, 0202, and 1602 50 originating in Poland.
